      <t>&lt;p&gt;This report attempts to summarize the key features of OSPF V2.  It also attempts to analyze how the protocol will perform and scale in the Internet.  This memo provides information for the Internet community.  It does not specify any Internet standard.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
